text: Landis Power Station is a natural gas-fired station owned by SaskPower, located in Landis, Saskatchewan, Canada and operated as a peaking plant. == Description == The Landis Station consists of:Plant Description * 1 - 79 MW unit, commissioned in 1975 and refurbished in 1999. == See also == * SaskPower ==References== == External links == * SaskPower Station Description Category:Natural gas-fired power stations in Saskatchewan Category:SaskPower Category:Reford No. 379, Saskatchewan
title: Landis Power Station
